											On this journey, we faced
the danger of crevasses,
											intense cold,
											so cold that sweat turns
to ice inside your clothing,
											your teeth can crack,
											water can freeze in your eyes.
											Let&#39;s just say it&#39;s a bit chilly.
(Laughter)
